gHMQC_d2:            Setup parameters for N15 gHMQC pulse sequence
			using decoupler 2  (M)

        syntex:         gHMQC_d2(<'GLIDE'>)
        Description:    Converts the current parameter set to
                        gHMQC experiment for N15 with decoupler 2
                        for N15.  If the argument GLIDE
                        is supplied, PROTON parameter set for that
                        particular sample is first retrived.
        Related:	gHMQC
        		gHMQC15
        
